reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Highly recommend. Has alot of neat features. Usb charging ports, space to put pens and of course the lamp that has three options for the light and four options for the brightness. The lamp is lightweight, but its fine. neck is very flexible. Using it next to me for bedside lamp.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute looking functional lamp
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I wanted a desk lamp for my work setup but my wife likes to keep things asthetic so I found this lamp which completely blends into our theme and also is super functional. The modes allow you to set the brightness and the quality overall is very good. It also has couple of usb ports. I use them to charge my powerbank or smart watch. Great addition to my desk setup!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good but Top-Heavy
reviews.reviewText: It's accurately described. A flexible neck, adjustable brightness, container for holding items, and USB ports are all useful features. However, be aware that the lamp is top heavy with a very light bottom. It will fall over and possibly onto a hard surface with the slightest jostling, and the top can't even be crooked in some positions because it will tip over. A possible solution is to place a small, dense, heavy item in the accessory holder or strap it down.

reviews.reviewText: I love it that has an outlet on it and 3 different light-style pen holders etc. I like it very much.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pretty desk lamp

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Multifunctional desk lamp
reviews.reviewText: Highly recommend this product. You get the usb charging ports, space to put pens or charging chords and of course the lamp that has three options for the light warmth and four options for the brightness of each. It’s super easy to use and has two buttons only that you need only touch to activate. The lamp itself is very elegant and of high quality. The neck is very flexible. I use it as a bed side lamp. It even has a little edge to hold the phone which is great!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Although the light looked pretty, it did not have the option to change colors as advertised. The only controls we have are power and brightness adjustment to 3 levels.I wish it had the cool white light and I would have kept it. Also, the USB ports are weirdly positioned on to front of the lamp and it would make the desk look so cluttered. with all those tangled USB cords. I feel it would have done a better job of hiding those cords if they were positioned on more of the back side of the lamp.If you like to keep your study table more organized and hate cords, this may not be for you.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Multi-functional and very sturdy
reviews.reviewText: This lamp works great. It had continuously adjustable brightness. The on/off and brightness buttons are sensitive enough. It has two pen holders, easy to organize. I have used it for more than 1 month. It serves the purpose I purchased it for. I really like it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Really happy with the lamp, 3 colour modes with adjustable brightness make it incredibly versatile for various tasks (from working to just relaxing). Even though it's mostly made of plastic, it seems sturdy and looks stylish, adding a modern touch to my workspace. Just the right size, it is handy to have a pencil holder, USB charging ports and lamp all in one - saves a to of space on a desk (tip: it can be used as a headphones holder as well :)). Great purchase
Eine sehr gute Schreibtischlampe. Meine Kinder mögen sie sehr. Die USB-Schnittstelle ist sehr praktisch.

Cette petite lampe est vraiment très belle, soigner et épuré elle fait vraiment très joli sur mon bureau.Elle est équipée d'un range stylo et de deux ports USB ce qui est très pratique sur un bureau.La lampe LED dispose de 3 réglages de luminosité ce qui est assez sympathique suivant l'usage qu'on fait de celle-ci.Elle est peut encombrante ce qui est un plus, je ne suis pas déçu et je pense qu'elle ne vous décevra pas.C'est un très bon achat que je ne regrette pas.

reviews.reviewText: It does not take up a lot of space and looks good with the rest of my desk.
